links/\">Links</a><a class=\"page-link\" href=\"/proofofwork/\">POW</a><a class=\"page-link\" href=\"/usesthis/\">Uses This</a></div>\n      </nav><div class=\"theme-switcher\">\n      <button class=\"theme-switcher__button\" onclick=\"toggleTheme()\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\" title=\"Toggle dark/light mode\">\n        <span class=\"theme-switcher__icon theme-switcher__icon--light\">‚òÄÔ∏è</span>\n        <span class=\"theme-switcher__icon theme-switcher__icon--dark\">üåô</span>\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n<main class=\"page-content\" aria-label=\"Content\">\n      <div class=\"wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"letter-container\">\n  <div class=\"letter-paper\">\n    <article class=\"post h-entry\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\">\n\n      <header class=\"post-header\">\n        <h1 class=\"post-title p-name\" itemprop=\"name headline\">Counter-positioning and self-imposed constraints on Twitter</h1>\n        <p class=\"post-meta\">\n          <time class=\"dt-published\" datetime=\"2022-01-04T00:00:00+00:00\" itemprop=\"datePublished\">Jan 4, 2022\n          </time></p>\n      </header>\n\n      <div class=\"post-content e-content\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n        <ol>\n  <li>Does not follow anyone, except wife. Did the same with another social network where he was slightly popular.</li>\n  <li>Deletes his tweets, no matter how much of a banger. Willingly gives up on distribution.</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/2020/01/17/twitter-rules.html\">Does not tag people</a>. People who tags others get banned. Willingly gives up on discovery of account.</li>\n  <li>Reminds people to not tag him regularly.</li>\n  <li>Avoids path dependence, by tweeting shit posts one day, <a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/2020/03/23/running-product-team.html\">playbooks</a> the next. Throws <a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/2021/09/24/things-no-one-tell-you.html\">red pills</a> the third day and on fourth day spews <a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/2022/01/02/path-dependence-overshoot.html\">random thoughts that has almost no TAM</a>.</li>\n  <li>Has never been part of any Twitter circlejerk. Rarely likes or comments on tweets of other accounts.</li>\n  <li>Avoids putting labels, even though it is the fastest way to grow followers point.</li>\n  <li>In a world where everyone is virtue signaling and gently patting themselves in the back, works hard, but also pats his back the hardest.</li>\n  <li>Dunks on <a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/2021/11/27/npc.html\">NPC reply bois</a>.</li>\n  <li>Blocks anyone who QTs to dunk.</li>\n  <li>Has probably muted half of the people already.</li>\n  <li>Rarely replies to comments on tweets.</li>\n  <li>Makes his Twitter a Sisyphean adventure that restarts everyday.</li>\n  <li>Never deployed popular growth tactics inspite of writing two playbooks on them: <a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/2021/03/17/social-media-playbook.html\">link</a>, <a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/2020/01/30/life-math-money.html\">link</a>.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>I wonder who is this person putting <a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/booksummaries/2017/07/17/understanding-porter-joan.html#:~:text=The%20Third%20Test%3A%20Trade%2Doffs\">self-imposed constraints</a> on himself and playing the <a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/booksummaries/2019/08/22/seven-powers-hamilton-helmer.html#:~:text=COUNTER%20POSITIONING%20%E2%80%94the%20third%20of%20the%207%20Powers\">counter-positioning</a> meta game on Twitter for years.</p>\n\n      </div><a class=\"u-url\" href=\"/2022/01/04/counterpositioning-constraints-social-media.html\" hidden></a>\n    </article>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n      </div>\n    </main><footer class=\"site-footer h-card\">\n  <data class=\"u-url\" href=\"/\"></data>\n\n  <div class=\"wrapper\">\n\n    <div class=\"footer-col-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"footer-col one-half\">\n      <p class=\"footer-heading\"> Powered by <a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com\">Jekyll</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/jekyll/minima\">Minima.</a> ¬© Manas J Saloi.</p>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col one-half\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n       <h4></h4>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n</footer>\n</body>\n\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+Pro:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n</html>\n", "crawl_time": 1751205350.5587158}